# Events — <%= appName %>

Domain event bus with in-process and Redis pub/sub support.

## Environment

```env
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
EVENTS_CHANNEL=<%= appName %>.events
```

## Usage

```typescript
import { eventBus } from './src/services/events/index.js';

eventBus.onEvent('user.created', async (event) => {
  console.log(event.payload);
});

await eventBus.publish('user.created', { userId: 1 });
await eventBus.subscribeRemote();
```
